# Entity Skill

## ΉΕνΈςΖ

ΉΔΙΈκεΉγ┤ JPA EntityΉβΑ RepositoryΈξ╝ ΊΦΕΈκεΉιζΊΛ╕ Ή╗ρΈ▓νΉΖαΉΩΡ ΈπηΆ▓Ν ΉηΣΉΕ▒ΊΧεΈΜν.

## ΉΜνΊΨΚ ΉιΙΉ░ρ

### 1. Entity ΉηΣΉΕ▒

ΉεΕΉ╣α: `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/entity/{ΈΠΕΈσΦΉζ╕}/`

```kotlin
@Entity
@Table(catalog = "{catalog}", name = "{table_name}")
class EntityName(
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(generator = "uuid2")
    @GenericGenerator(name = "uuid2", strategy = "uuid2")
    val id: String = "",

    // Έ╣ΕΉοΙΈΜΙΉΛν ΊΧΕΈΥε
    val userId: String,
    val name: String,

    // Ά┤ΑΆ│Ε ΈπνΊΧΣ (ΊΧΕΉγΦΉΜε)
    @ManyToOne(fetch = FetchType.LAZY)
    @JoinColumn(name = "category_id", referencedColumnName = "code")
    val category: CategoryEntity? = null,

    // Ά░ΡΉΓυ ΊΧΕΈΥε
    @CreatedDate
    @Column(columnDefinition = "datetime(3)", nullable = false, updatable = false)
    var createdAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),

    @LastModifiedDate
    var updatedAt: LocalDateTime = LocalDateTime.now(),
)
```

### 2. Repository ΉηΣΉΕ▒

ΉεΕΉ╣α: `domain/src/main/kotlin/com/maum/backend/repository/{ΈΠΕΈσΦΉζ╕}/`

```kotlin
interface EntityNameRepository : JpaRepository<EntityName, String> {
    fun findByUserId(userId: String): List<EntityName>
    fun findByUserIdAndStatus(userId: String, status: Int): List<EntityName>
}
```

### 3. Catalog ΉΕιΊΔζ

| Catalog | ΈΠΕΈσΦΉζ╕ |
|---------|--------|
| `maum` | user, profile, call, product, follow |
| `moment` | post, moment, comment, like |
| `chat` | chat_room |
| `notification` | notification, notification_setting |

### 4. Ή╗┤ΊΝΝΉζ╝ ΊβΧΉζ╕

```bash
./gradlew :domain:compileKotlin
```

## Ήμ╝ΉζαΉΓυΊΧφ

- EntityΈΛΦ `var` Ή╡εΉΗΝΊβΦ, Έ│ΑΆ▓╜ ΊΧΕΉγΦΊΧε ΊΧΕΈΥεΈπΝ `var`
- `@Table`Ήζα `catalog`ΈΛΦ ΉΜνΉιε DB Ή╣┤ΊΔΙΈκεΆ╖╕ΈςΖΆ│╝ Ήζ╝Ή╣α
- `@JoinColumn`Ήζα `referencedColumnName`ΉζΕ ΈςΖΉΜεΉιΒΉε╝Έκε ΉπΑΉιΧ (Ά╕░Έ│╕Ά░Τ `id`Ά░Α ΉΧΕΈΜΝ Ά▓╜Ήγ░)
- ΉΨΣΈ░σΊΨξ Ά┤ΑΆ│ΕΈ│┤ΈΜν ΈΜρΈ░σΊΨξ Ά┤ΑΆ│Ε Ήγ░ΉΕι
